{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1520,"text":"Hannah is excited to be going to college."},{"time":4960,"text":"She couldn't wait\nto get out of her parents' house,"},{"time":7760,"text":"to prove to them that she's an adult,"},{"time":9800,"text":"and to prove to her new friends\nthat she belongs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13360,"text":"She heads to a campus party"},{"time":14960,"text":"where she sees a guy\nthat she has a crush on."},{"time":17520,"text":"Let's call him Mike."},{"time":20440,"text":"The next day, Hannah wakes up\nwith a pounding headache."},{"time":25280,"text":"She can only remember\nthe night in flashes."},{"time":28480,"text":"But what she does remember is"},{"time":30200,"text":"throwing up in the hall\noutside Mike's room"},{"time":34440,"text":"and staring at the wall silently\nwhile he was inside her,"},{"time":37560,"text":"wanting it to stop,"},{"time":39520,"text":"then shakily stumbling home."},{"time":42856,"text":"She doesn't feel good about what happened,"},{"time":44880,"text":"but she thinks, \"Maybe this is just\nwhat sex in college is?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":49840,"text":"One in five women and one in 13 men\nwill be sexually assaulted"},{"time":54080,"text":"at some point during their college career\nin the United States."},{"time":59520,"text":"Less than 10 percent will ever report\ntheir assault to their school"},{"time":63960,"text":"or to the police."},{"time":65480,"text":"And those who do, on average,\nwait 11 months to make the report."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72040,"text":"Hannah initially just feels like dealing\nwith what happened on her own."},{"time":75760,"text":"But when she sees Mike\ntaking girls home from parties,"},{"time":78360,"text":"she's worried about them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":80600,"text":"After graduation, Hannah learns"},{"time":82880,"text":"that she was one of five women\nwho Mike did the exact same thing to."},{"time":88840,"text":"And this is not an unlikely scenario"},{"time":91280,"text":"because 90 percent of sexual assaults"},{"time":94360,"text":"are committed by repeat offenders."},{"time":97160,"text":"But with such low reporting rates,"},{"time":98840,"text":"it's fairly unlikely that even\nrepeat perpetrators will be reported,"},{"time":102680,"text":"much less anything happen if they are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105240,"text":"In fact, only six percent\nof assaults reported to the police"},{"time":110400,"text":"end with the assailant\nspending a single day in prison."},{"time":113680,"text":"Meaning, there's a 99 percent chance\nthat they'll get away with it."},{"time":119400,"text":"This means there's practically\nno deterrent to assault"},{"time":122840,"text":"in the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126160,"text":"Now, I'm an infectious disease\nepidemiologist by training."},{"time":129520,"text":"I'm interested in systems and networks"},{"time":132640,"text":"and where we can concentrate\nour resources to do the most good."},{"time":137200,"text":"So this, to me, is a tragic\nbut a solvable problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143280,"text":"So when the issue of campus assault\nstarted hitting the news a few years ago,"},{"time":147440,"text":"it felt like a unique opportunity\nto make a change."},{"time":150840,"text":"And so we did."},{"time":152560,"text":"We started by talking\nto college survivors."},{"time":155360,"text":"And what they wish they'd had\nin college is pretty simple;"},{"time":158880,"text":"they wanted a website,"},{"time":160440,"text":"one they could use\nat the time and place"},{"time":162600,"text":"that felt safest to them"},{"time":164800,"text":"with clearly written information\nabout their reporting options,"},{"time":168800,"text":"with the ability to electronically\nreport their assault,"},{"time":171960,"text":"rather than having the first step"},{"time":173600,"text":"to go in and talk to someone\nwho may or may not believe them."},{"time":177080,"text":"With the option to create\na secure, timestamped document"},{"time":180400,"text":"of what happened to them,"},{"time":181920,"text":"preserving evidence\neven if they don't want to report yet."},{"time":185560,"text":"And lastly, and perhaps most critically,"},{"time":188560,"text":"with the ability to report their assault"},{"time":190600,"text":"only if someone else\nreported the same assailant."},{"time":194920,"text":"You see, knowing that you weren't\nthe only one changes everything."},{"time":198080,"text":"It changes the way\nyou frame your own experience,"},{"time":200440,"text":"it changes the way\nyou think about your perpetrator,"},{"time":202920,"text":"it means that if you do come forward,"},{"time":204760,"text":"you'll have someone else's back\nand they'll have yours."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208840,"text":"We created a website\nthat actually does this"},{"time":211360,"text":"and we launched it [...] in August,"},{"time":214400,"text":"on two college campuses."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216600,"text":"And we included a unique matching system"},{"time":219520,"text":"where if Mike's first victim\nhad come forward,"},{"time":222480,"text":"saved her record,\nentered into the matching system"},{"time":225280,"text":"and named Mike,"},{"time":226560,"text":"and Mike's second victim\nhad done the same thing"},{"time":228960,"text":"a few months later,"},{"time":230640,"text":"they would have matched"},{"time":232000,"text":"and the verified contact information\nof both survivors"},{"time":235520,"text":"would have been sent\nto the authorities at the same time"},{"time":238280,"text":"for investigation and follow up."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241600,"text":"If a system like this had existed\nfor Hannah and her peers,"},{"time":245320,"text":"it's more likely\nthat they would have reported,"},{"time":247880,"text":"that they would have been believed,"},{"time":249680,"text":"and that Mike would have been\nkicked off campus,"},{"time":251960,"text":"gone to jail, or at least\ngotten the help that he needed."},{"time":255920,"text":"And if we were able to stop\nrepeat offenders like Mike"},{"time":259440,"text":"after just their second assault\nfollowing a match,"},{"time":263080,"text":"survivors like Hannah\nwould never even be assaulted"},{"time":265720,"text":"in the first place."},{"time":267760,"text":"We could prevent\n59 percent of sexual assaults"},{"time":271880,"text":"just by stopping\nrepeat perpetrators earlier on."},{"time":276080,"text":"And because we're creating\na real deterrent to assault,"},{"time":278800,"text":"for perhaps the first time,"},{"time":280960,"text":"maybe the Mikes of the world\nwould never even try to assault anyone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":286640,"text":"The type of system I'm describing,"},{"time":288640,"text":"the type of system that survivors want"},{"time":291040,"text":"is a type of information escrow,"},{"time":293600,"text":"meaning an entity that holds on\nto information for you"},{"time":296840,"text":"and only releases it to a third party"},{"time":299320,"text":"when certain pre-agreed upon\nconditions are met,"},{"time":301920,"text":"such as a match."},{"time":303600,"text":"The application that we built\nis for college campuses."},{"time":307360,"text":"But the same type of system\ncould be used in the military"},{"time":310440,"text":"or even the workplace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313720,"text":"We don't have to live in a world"},{"time":316280,"text":"where 99 percent of rapists\nget away with it."},{"time":320120,"text":"We can create one"},{"time":321560,"text":"where those who do wrong\nare held accountable,"},{"time":324520,"text":"where survivors get the support\nand justice they deserve,"},{"time":327960,"text":"where the authorities\nget the information they need,"},{"time":330880,"text":"and where there's a real deterrent"},{"time":332800,"text":"to violating the rights\nof another human being."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337120,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":338360,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}